{"tid":1299960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯：冀協助年輕人行「正道」","createTime":"2019-07-09T08:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:11:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":247,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"95dfe8bed9a3cf5a037fd3af868118d22b646dbb","tid":1299960,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1466793_1_L_20190705171735.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1466793_1_L_20190705171735.jpg&h=808da596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗中午在官邸宴請部分建制派立法會議員。<br />\n<br />\n有份出席的議員何君堯表示，適逢近日屬「多事之秋」，月初又發生衝擊及破壞立法會大樓事件，大家在會上都表示關心，包括應如何關顧年輕人的利益、上流發展空間等，他引述張建宗說，希望議員提出意見，可納入10月發表的《施政報告》。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯又說，他認為應在幾個範疇處理年輕人問題，包括在教育、社工支援上要做得更好更廣，另外亦可尋求宗教領袖協助，讓年輕人行「正道」，不要太偏執。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466793-20190705.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466793-20190705.htm&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1X4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=abf8270a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466793-20190705.htm&h=1203d102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466793-20190705.htm</a>"},{"pid":"07979b90cc07d6645a8527444d46cf9fcf508362","tid":1299960,"uid":263261,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:20:08.000Z","msg":"呢條仆街好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44a2622320cbfe9bf144936576b570d536a6c6d","tid":1299960,"uid":276274,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:21:06.000Z","msg":"佢落咗去（地獄）未？"},{"pid":"bf2d541cb4afc63176bd5a937940020eb77ca3f2","tid":1299960,"uid":243691,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:21:16.000Z","msg":"唔係係度派！！！"},{"pid":"686d9eb16aa7882